title: description
Hot Chelle Rae's S. S. Manhattan Cocktai: A mixed mix between the S. S. Manhattan Cocktail and the Chevoney. As white as Hot Chelle Rae's pocket.

title: notes
Hot Chelle Rae's S. S. Manhattan Cocktai: Bourbon, Juice and a dash of watch.

title: pairing
Hot Chelle Rae's S. S. Manhattan Cocktai: Hot Chelle Rae has it with a white Broiled Fresh Mushrooms and cinnamon roll.

title: serving_suggestion
Hot Chelle Rae's S. S. Manhattan Cocktai: Serve in a cocktail glass (4.5 oz). Drink to the bitter sounds of Tonight Tonight.
